  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Log Management</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loio667acb53f0f67314e10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Log Management </h1><div class=\"body\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Use</span></p>\n<p class=\"p\"> Every function or application (for example, import of feeder system data) creates an application log that can be used to control internal system processes.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">You can display the statutory reporting logs by choosing <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Log Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Display</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span> (transaction <span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">SLG1</span>) with object <span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">ISSR</span>. In a similar way, you delete logs by choosing <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Log Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Delete</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span> (transaction <span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">SLG2</span>) with object <span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">ISSR</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\"> For data import functions outside of Customizing, you also have the option to create more detailed logs in the system by using the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Detailed Log</span> indicator.</p>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
}